    "The main conclusions emphasize the integration of detection methods with social media platforms, the potential of distributed ledger technology, and the promotion of explainable AI for effective understanding and utilization of information.",
    "The work in Tolosana et al. (2020) reviews techniques for manipulating face images, including deepfake methods, as well as tools for detecting such manipulations.",
    "Four types of facial manipulation are discussed: entire face synthesis, identity swap, attribute manipulation, and expression swap.",
    "For each group, the paper provides details on techniques, existing databases, and key benchmarks.",
